Police raided Alan Greaves' home in Colne, Lancashire in September 2013 .
The father-of-eight claimed 'the Illuminati' framed him by downloading child abuse images on his computer .
He was also a full-time carer for his disabled sister aged just 10 .
Judge Simon Newell said there appeared to be sexually-explicit images .
Greaves pleaded guilty to two offences of making indecent images .